1984;;Ninja III: The Domination;;American;;Sam Firstenberg;;Sho Kosugi, Lucinda Dickey;;action;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ninja_III:_The_Domination;;A telephone linewoman who teaches aerobics classes[1] is possessed by an evil spirit of a fallen ninja when coming to his aid. The spirit seeks revenge on those who killed him and uses the female instructor's body to carry out his mission. The only way the spirit will leave the aerobic instructor's body is through combat with another ninja.